      "content": "I see. So when you talk about \"different cultural expectations\" and \"community friction,\" are you suggesting that certain demographics are fundamentally harder to integrate or more likely to negatively impact property values and neighborhood cohesion? Like, is there a specific profile of demographic change that's more \"risky\" than others?",
